    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《微型战场》是怎样的游戏？</strong></h2>这款战斗飞行模拟游戏来源于开发者的热爱，力图在模拟性与易玩性之间寻找一个完美的平衡点。我们要用独特的画风展现一场虚构的冷战时代冲突。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1347550/extras/0f49efcfe439b5d2f7a573ae41125326.poster.avif?t=1750942325\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1347550/extras/0f49efcfe439b5d2f7a573ae41125326.webm?t=1750942325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1347550/extras/0f49efcfe439b5d2f7a573ae41125326.mp4?t=1750942325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻度战斗飞行模拟</h2>《微型战场》完全聚焦于飞行、狗斗与近距离空中支援的乐趣。模拟元素的加入是为了有乐趣与深度的游戏体验，而非单纯追求真实性。游戏包含源自模拟器的机制，比如在目标上方发射导弹以提高射程，这样你就可以探索大量的战术。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1347550/extras/08128e2adb07f12916fc57212da7a8cc.avif?t=1750942325\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装备管理</h2>快武装好你的飞机。导弹、机炮、炸弹：为每个任务选择适合的装备。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1347550/extras/d5480287138914c86c97320575a6f5b0.avif?t=1750942325\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速任务生成器</h2>在《微型战场》中，你可以快速设计各类任务并驾机投身其中，在美丽的风景中悠闲飞行，选择两队飞机进行狗斗，或是攻击和支援地面单位，完成打击任务。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1347550/extras/e13c823d8890e73acad04cfd74ddeba9.avif?t=1750942325\" width=616 height=376 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战场模式</h2>在战略地图上计划行动：选择目标，识别威胁，选择支援单位，影响战局。你身处战争的中心，你的加入将影响战果。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1347550/extras/b8dac4d293f7562f8962d429fbbd0f8b.avif?t=1750942325\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >详细实用的数据库</h2>内置的数据库不仅能显示车辆、飞机和武器的详细参数，还能提供追击不同飞机和应对各种威胁的战术指导。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1347550/extras/bce9b7907f1f73d395fcf285fbb82c86.avif?t=1750942325\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
